{"tid":1718292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地有無總結到...呢個經驗?","createTime":"2019-11-13T22:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T22:21:33.000Z","uid":270860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7ce753ed0334b46a96d5d035ac78bed7b3d794d9","tid":1718292,"uid":270860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T22:07:20.000Z","msg":"8月5日大罷工，粗略估計20萬人參加，100班航班取消，先唔講之後嘅秋後算帳，或係唔係真係做成大影響。<br />\n<br />\n經驗係... <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">各行各業會 show 職員 PASS 去某個 TG, 集中令參加者大概知道有幾多人一齊罷，先有個信心參加罷工。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢班人甚至要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>組織起黎</strong></span></span>，未來要再發動罷工去<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">抵抗老闆嘅白色恐怖</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n連呢 d 係基本都無，發生罷工嘅機率更低。<br />\n<br />\n所以運動要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">有意識地， 改變策略</span></span></strong>，不是前線，而係 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">面向打工仔</span></span></strong> !"},{"pid":"06c4cb5ec36c2124ea14721b22c065eefc534658","tid":1718292,"uid":270860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T22:10:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"265f10b61f0486919d33578810fffeaec14ab9a5","tid":1718292,"uid":270860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T22:14:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03f1614e13a24d0399b2247e5bcdaec06767f99f","tid":1718292,"uid":270860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T22:15:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"439628190ff4e3e3f89636ae124e27ddf24e39d9","tid":1718292,"uid":270860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T22:15:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"279c044a6fa683201d45b730203b15590f077fa8","tid":1718292,"uid":270860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T22:16:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39951ee57914961c42f20e